data.description:
Ask Agent for details about Assumable loan or Special loan types for this property! Seller is also offering a home warranty. 
Discover this charming home nestled in Independence! 

Boasting 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, a detached garage, fenced yard, and modern interior updates, this residence offers comfort and convenience. Additionally, its spacious driveway provides ample parking, all situated at the rear of the lot for enhanced privacy.

Notable attribute of the property encompasses a feasible loan arrangement. Contact agent regarding the financing incentives. Furthermore, the seller is offering a warranty.
